flowchart LR
  A[Start<br>processing audit<br>file] --> B[Load row<br>from file]

  B --> C{Already in<br>CiviCRM?}

%% Branch: Not in CiviCRM
  C -- No --> D[Lookup in<br>Smashpig/logs]
  D --> E{Lookup<br>successful?}
  E -- No --> G1[Skip row<br>no log]
  E -- Yes --> H[Transaction<br>type]
  H -- Positive --> I[Queue donation<br>creation]
  H -- Negative --> J[Queue refund<br>creation]
  H -- Fee --> K[Create fee<br>contribution]

%% Branch: Already in CiviCRM
  C -- Yes --> L{Settlement batch<br>assigned?}
  L -- Yes --> G2[Skip row<br>already settled]
  L -- No --> M[Queue settlement<br>update]

%% Merge processing
  G1 --> N[Row<br>processed]
  G2 --> N
  I --> N
  J --> N
  K --> N
  M --> N

%% File-level logic
  N --> O{More rows<br>in file?}
  O -- Yes --> B
  O -- No --> P{All rows<br>already in<br>CiviCRM?}

  P -- Yes --> Q[Move file<br>to Completed]
  P -- No --> S[Payout info exists<br>for batch + currency?]
  Q --> S

%% Batch-level logic
  S -- No --> T[Set batch<br>status Open]
  S -- Yes --> U{Row sums<br>equal payout?}
  U -- No --> V[Set status Open<br>and alert fr-tech]
  U -- Yes --> W[Set status total<br>verified and lock]

  V --> X[End]
  W --> X
